## ğŸ“Œ Features
âœ… **Automated UI Testing** for **SupportGoWhere** payout calculator  
âœ… **Cross-browser testing** using Selenium WebDriver  
âœ… **Data-driven testing** using Cucumber Scenarios & Examples  
